location.fullValue: Carissa Plan, Estates at La Cuentista

data.description: Price reduced !!!! With stunning views of the Sandias. Owned Solar panels!!  Well maintained 5/6 bedroom home nestled in a quiet NW neighborhood. Large kitchen with island, stainless steel appliances, BF Nook, and plenty of counter space and cabinets. 2 living areas, formal dining, and spacious bedrooms. Huge primary bedroom with walk-in closet, beautiful bath, and balcony ,Low maintenance backyard with covered patio and synthetic grass. RV parking on the side yard with 50 amp hookup. Convenient location with nearby shopping, dining, parks, and walking distance to the Petroglyphs. 2 refrigerated AC units. Newer Roof,  remodeled baths (downstairs and 1 upstairs), luxury vinyl floors, gates and balcony railing. Schedule a showing today to see this amazing home!
